    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like such a heavy weight to carry. i'm so tired of trying to be something, to exist, when it all feels so hollow. you make it sound so... inevitable. like there's no point in even trying to hold on if the end is just going to be this silence anyway.",
